Package: cctu
Type: Package
Title: In-house Functions for Report Writing at Cambridge Clinical Trials Unit
Version: 0.7.0
Date: 2022-04-13
Author: Simon Bond, Alimu Dayimu
Maintainer: Simon Bond <simon.bond@addenbrookes.nhs.uk>
Description: Several useful functions and a vignette to explain how to put it all together. Notably, it produces word documents via xml, and deals with ensuring the correct population is used.
